::Demise/EndBringer/Greven::

Demise, EndBringer, and Greven stop half a mile away from the new 
bots, examining them using scanners. EndBringer activates his comm.

"New bots, we come in peace." He says into it, directing the 
transmission at them. "Are we welcome to approach?"

around.
